---
title: Spring Gnocchi Cacio e Pepe with Fresh Salad
description: We've taken the classic Italian pasta dish and given it a little seasonal twist! Fresh asparagus, peas, and seared gnocchi in a creamy pepper sauce alongside a fresh garden salad show you that some of the best meals only take a few humble ingredients!
